# Project Memory — InstaGold (Gold)

> **Read `ARCHITECTURE.md` for the full system design.** This file is a quick reference.

## App Identity
- App name: **InstaGold**
- Android package (applicationId): `com.ibrahym.goldfamily` (do NOT change)
- Android namespace: `com.ibrahym.instagold`
- iOS bundle ID: `com.ibrahym.goldtracker`
- Firebase project: `goldcalculate`
- **Build commands ALWAYS require `--flavor dev|prod`** for Android

## Architecture (Apr 2026)
- Monorepo: `scraper-service/` (dormant), `main-backend/` (LIVE on Railway), `flutter-app/`
- **Backend is LIVE** at `https://backend-production-c042.up.railway.app` — deploy via `cd main-backend && railway up`
- Mobile mode: local SQLite for most CRUD + direct eDahab scraping for prices
- **Price alerts and FCM device registration go through the Railway backend via HTTP** — NOT local SQLite
- Web mode: talks to main-backend HTTP APIs

## Notifications — How They Actually Work
- **FCM is ACTIVE** — Railway backend sends push at Cairo 07:00/11:00/15:00/19:00 via `notificationsScheduler.js`
- `FCM_SUMMARIES_ENABLED=true` and `MIN_FCM_CLIENT_BUILD=2` in Railway env
- `push_notifications_service.dart` registers devices with backend on first launch
- `isFcmActive()` returns true when backend confirms — local notifications self-disable
- **Local notifications are FALLBACK only** — they auto-activate if backend is unreachable
- **iOS before Apple Developer/APNs:** do NOT show foreground notification banners on app open/resume. App open/resume only refreshes prices + widget data. iOS local notifications come from `ios_background_fetch.dart` only, and only when iOS wakes the app and prices changed meaningfully.
- **iOS widget:** best-effort only while app is closed. It refreshes immediately on app open/resume and on iOS background-fetch wakes; do not promise real-time widget updates without APNs/FCM.
- **Price threshold alerts** — user creates via bell icon, backend checks on price sync, sends FCM push
- Two Android channels: `price_updates` (daily, mutable) and `price_alerts` (threshold, max priority)

## Key Data Flow Rules
| Data | Mobile source | Backend involved? |
|---|---|---|
| Prices for display | Local `GoldScraper` + SQLite | No |
| Members, assets, savings, goals | Local SQLite | No |
| Price alerts CRUD | HTTP to Railway backend | **Yes** |
| FCM device registration | HTTP to Railway backend | **Yes** |
| Slot notifications | FCM from Railway (primary) / local (fallback) | **Yes** |

## STRICT Design Rules (MANDATORY)

### Logo
- Use ONLY the provided IG monogram image (`assets/icons/ig_logo.png`)
- Logo in: app header, login screen, splash, empty states, launcher icon

### Dark Mode (must NOT be flat)
- Base: `#0B0B0D` with layered gradients
- Wave patterns via `PremiumBackground` widget
- Radial gold glow highlights
- **FAIL condition: flat black background = WRONG**

### Gold Styling
- Primary: `#D4AF37`, deep `#C9A227`, light `#E8CD5A`, muted `#B8962E`
- Always gradient gold, never flat

