## Savings/Goals Features (Apr 2026)
- Weight inputs use `numberWithOptions(decimal: true)` — decimal grams work on all keyboards
- `PurchaseGoals` DB has `manufacturing_price_g REAL DEFAULT 0` column (DB version 4, migrated from v3)
- Goal add/edit forms: optional manufacturing price field (مصنعية, EGP/g)
- Gold Calculator `ExpansionTile` between savings and goals sections:
  - Inputs: karat, weight (g), manufacturing EGP/g, taxes % (default 10)
  - Live outputs: price without adds, total adds (mfg + tax), price with adds
  - "Add to Goals" button → choose with/without adds price → `createGoal(overrideTargetPrice: ...)`

